title: [Grawood Farmstead, Field]
description: Stretching across the length of several large fields, tall green artichoke plants fill the eye with their voluminous growth.  At this corner of the field, the harvest of the plant has already started, as evidenced by the short, headless lengths of stem attached to the main stalks.
paths: Obvious paths: north, northeast, east, southwest
room.location: Grawood Farmstead outside of River's Rest
